Package org.sopra.api.command

Interface Command

All Known Subinterfaces:
AdjustConsumerCommand, AdjustmentCommand, AdjustProducerCommand, BuildPowerPlantCommand, UpgradeLineCommand
public interface Command
Commands are used to change the state of a scenario. They can be used to build power plants, upgrade power lines or regulate controllable energy nodes. This interface is the superclass of all command interfaces in the API.
